{"address":"0x0B20ED7418f153a6595E0F88c682DF52d54B00c4","signedPayload":"{
	"for": "nouns-agora",
	"delegateStatement": "My focus within NounsDAO is on proliferation, community building and onboarding of new creative prop builders into the DAO. ‚åê‚óß-‚óß\n\nI am the Prop Builder behind [Proposal 110: Nouns On The Ground 6 Month Proliferation Pod](https://nouns.wtf/vote/110) and attend events in the US and abroad connecting both crypto natives and newbies in the space to NounsDAO. ‚åê‚ô•-‚ô•\n\nI am a [Nouncil](https://nouncil.wtf) member and active host for the daily [Noun O' Clock](https://www.nounoclock.app) twitter space that helps involve the community in picking the next Noun after each auction settles. These spaces have recently begun live streaming on YouTube where I am involved in additional video/media content focused on Nouns education and proliferation. ‚åê‚ìù¬∞‚ìí\n\nI am an original member of [FOODNOUNS DAO](https://www.foodnouns.wtf/), a subDAO forked from NounsDAO. There are 3 daily FOODNOUNS auctions that contribute 25% per auction directly to the NounsDAO Treasury. ü•ë\n\nI host a weekly AUA: Ask Us Anything with [toadyhawk.‚åê‚óß-‚óß](https://www.nounsagora.com/delegate/toadyhawk.%E2%8C%90%E2%97%A8-%E2%97%A8) in the [NounsDAO Discord](https://discord.gg/nouns) to help individuals who are just entering the ecosystem understand how they contribute or become future builders for the DAO. üó£Ô∏è\n\nAdditionally, I try to make myself available for individuals who need feedback on proposals being submitted to [Prop House](https://prop.house) and NSFW since encouraging builders and helping to \"nounify\" props is something I truly enjoy. I also hold NFTS (votes) in various nounish communities, including [Lil Nouns](https://lilnouns.wtf) - [Gnars DAO](https://gnars.wtf) - [FOODNOUNS DAO](https://www.foodnouns.wtf), and actively participate in their governance. ü§ù\n\nI am honored to have been recently delegated Noun 309 ü§ñüí≠ by [evets.eth](https://twitter.com/stevefink). Being able to actively participate in the on-chain governance has been a goal of mine since entering the community and I hope to maintain a strong and uplifting voice within this space. I would love to represent the vote of additional Nouns and can keep open communication about each Prop with anyone who delegates. ü´° ",
