{"address":"0x1e66a3D0a6A327b1F29e8ACf3a3d9E1E4E088683","signedPayload":"{
	"for": "nouns-agora",
	"delegateStatement": "**As your delegate I will thoughtfully review proposals, vote, and not waste treasury.**\n**Sam Ellis thepencil.eth**\n**Half owner of Noun #455** (Crane)\n**Delegate Nouns #67** (Baseball)\n**Serves on Nouncil** \n**Lil Nouner #749, 1324, 5738**\n**Gnar #516, 518, 575, 576**\n**NSFW POD Member**\n***A builder that co-launched various Noun extension projects***\n\n**As your Delegate** \n**I will:**\n- vote\n- thoughtfully review proposals\n- participate in discussions\n- relay info to the DAO on your behalf\n\n**I will not:**\n- waste treasury\n\nUltimately we should pass things that are best for the DAO and its members, the treasury is ours, and we should do what is in our best interest. We can't always just give it away or we won't be able to fund the projects that will really grow our treasury or build the public goods that make us say \"Hell Yes\". \n\n**I believe 4156 said it best**\n*I think we should be bold with the Nouns DAO treasury. We should fund and cultivate a community of builders by experimenting, taking risks, and ultimately funding every high quality proposal that could lead to interesting culture and software (especially ‚Äòmiddleware‚Äô) on the Nouns protocol*:\n- Centralized and decentralized APIs (let‚Äôs turn Noun o‚Äôclock into an internet-wide event)\n- Artwork that adds something new to the cultural conversation\n- Integrations with other Ethereum primitives and dapps\n- iOS and Android apps\n- Hackathons and Documentation\n- Things we‚Äôve never seen before\n\n*I think we have a historic opportunity ‚Äî to be bold, take risks, and ultimately attract the builders who can take the raw ingredients of the Nouns protocol, and turn them into applications that are ready to be consumed by the world. If we can do this, the DAO will attract more capital and higher quality participants, and the virtuous cycle will be complete.*\n\n**Previous accomplishments in the proliferation of Nouns:**\n‚åê‚ó®-‚ó®     Participated in the first days of testing nouns on Rinkeby\n‚åê‚ó®-‚ó®     [Active Nouncil member that regularly participates in voting](https://nouncil.wtf/)\n‚åê‚ó®-‚ó®     [Active participant and on the organizing committee for The Noun Square](https://twitter.com/noun_o_clock)\n‚åê‚ó®-‚ó®     [Participant in the funded Prop 70 (CC0 Pitchbook)](https://nouns.wtf/vote/70)\n‚åê‚ó®-‚ó®     [Co-developed NounsTown](https://nounstown.wtf/)\n‚åê‚ó®-‚ó®     [Co-developed YOLO Nouns](https://yolonouns.wtf/)\n‚åê‚ó®-‚ó®     [Co-developed Nouns Auction Tracker](https://auctions.wtf/)\n‚åê‚ó®-‚ó®     [Co-developed Composables](https://composables.wtf/)\n‚åê‚ó®-‚ó®     [Co-developed Nounish Labs](https://nounishlabs.wtf/)\n‚åê‚ó®-‚ó®     [Introduced Samsung to Nouns *(through Joey at Buoy Studio)* which lead to their video in Times Square and 837X DCL experience.](https://www.samsung.com/us/explore/metaverse-837x/)\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Kamhh0c.jpg)\nI do believe the DAO should be making highly sharable content that invites others to participate.",
